responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "020988914540E471757914A41DA180BE", "It\'s the Circle of Stones found in the lowlands. There is a tablet there written in an ancient script. It\'s surrounded by the Ashen Flame, but once we can interpret it, we\'ll know more about the ring from when it was intact, of which we only see the destroyed bits here. Those ruins date back to the end of Titan stewardship, and the origin of the gift sent from the scions themselves.")
